{
  "stem": "15082.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "On Sunday, we got worried that the Germans might come back, you know, because there was moving back and forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In fact, the Germans had fortified themselves just about 10 kilometers outside of Podkamien.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we felt the best thing to do was to start moving further away from there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And most of the few Jews that survived, and even the Polish man, Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Marczeniek was frightened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We all started moving back towards [INAUDIBLE], which was about, I'd say, 30 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was like an exodus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I would recall probably about 100 people going towards Krzemieniec.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We arrived there sometimes on Monday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were still not happy to stay there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We figured to go in a little bit further, deeper, away from the front lines, because we heard that Brody, which was almost parallel, it's really bad.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The Russians cannot make any headway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we went in as far as Dubno, which was a town that my mother's sister got married lived there in Dubno.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We got to Dubno about a day and a half later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A horse and wagon, and mostly walking, because there wasn't enough wagons at take us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So those that were able, were just walking behind the wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got to Dubno.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Again, we came into town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The town was completely no Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had hoped that maybe that we'd find my mother's sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We realized that that's not going to come to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew where she lived, because they were a very wealthy family that she married into.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had a big wholesale grocery business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the only one that we were-- came upon, is a-- her husband's [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] nephew that survived.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His name was Jack.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
